(86, 68, 22, '[{\"text\":\"Pink\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"68\",\"name\":\"Didik Yudiono\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/null\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-21T03:41:40.210Z\",\"_id\":\"545a7058-4f74-4f4f-9c13-cbbc305288c9\"},{\"text\":\"Ok\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"22\",\"name\":\"GONO\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/22ID1667528805_9f58b672-328d-4658-8a46-cc58426bcc36.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-21T03:47:07.832Z\",\"_id\":\"ce607f8b-5668-4de8-ba7a-b3d82e1d6e2d\"},{\"text\":\"Bagaimana pak cara mengatasi setelah  kerdil hampa\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"68\",\"name\":\"Didik Yudiono\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/68ID1669002396_656dccda-0c63-4b6d-867c-82c8d589ee19.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-21T05:30:06.932Z\",\"_id\":\"55e74e1f-cdfa-4b0c-af58-639322cffb02\"},{\"text\":\"Kalau sudah terserang kerdil hampa tidak bisa di atasi. Kerdil hampa bisanya di cegah hewan fektornya yaitu hama wereng coklat . Segera kedalikan. Yang kedua buat media tumbuh tanaman padi ber PH netal (6 -\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"22\",\"name\":\"GONO\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/22ID1667528805_9f58b672-328d-4658-8a46-cc58426bcc36.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-21T16:50:42.791Z\",\"_id\":\"224f9bda-be6c-46f1-9a47-c8c8349c3a15\"},{\"text\":\"PH netral (6-7)\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"22\",\"name\":\"GONO\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/22ID1667528805_9f58b672-328d-4658-8a46-cc58426bcc36.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-21T16:52:58.932Z\",\"_id\":\"f05f4eae-aaeb-488e-b7f5-c87d03f41bf7\"},{\"text\":\"Semprot tanah bekas kerdil rumput dan kerdil hampa dengan bubur California. Yaitu gamping 2 kg dan belerang 1 kg.dicampur dg air 10 liter. Digodok di masak tinggal 5 liter air di saring . Ampasnya di tabur dilahan. Kemudian air saringannya di sempurnakan kelahan dengan dosis air saringannya 250cc untuk satu tangki 15 liter air. 600 liter 1 hekter.\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"22\",\"name\":\"GONO\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/22ID1667528805_9f58b672-328d-4658-8a46-cc58426bcc36.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-22T02:25:23.614Z\",\"_id\":\"cf0ce15e-5bab-449f-a6d2-48338e708d92\"},{\"text\":\"Disempurnakan= disemprotkan\",\"user\":{\"_id\":\"22\",\"name\":\"GONO\",\"avatar\":\"https://siketan.com/upload/profile/22ID1667528805_9f58b672-328d-4658-8a46-cc58426bcc36.PNG\"},\"createdAt\":\"2022-11-22T02:27:38.544Z\",\"_id\":\"81d2ef67-3cdc-4720-9a1e-604ed282b378\"}]', '2022-11-21 03:41:41', '2022-11-22 09:27:39'),
